,"created":1752844008000,"text":"OpenGeoSys","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlsq6lktc0","created":1753087906553,"text":"OpenGeoSys是德国亥姆霍兹中心基于FEM开发的模拟器，能够模拟多孔和裂隙介质中的单一或耦合THMC(热、水文、机械和化学耦合模型)过程","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqg9jk0","created":1752844008000,"text":"PHREEQC","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlscdhgtc0","created":1753087876494,"text":"PHREEQC是一款基于离子结合水模型的地球化学反应计算软件，能够模拟GCS中的地球化学逆过程和一维输运反应。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqglb40","created":1752844008000,"text":"MIN3P","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlx2njlw80","created":1753088247156,"text":"用于研究地下水和土壤污染的三维多相多组分反应运移模型。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqg6jk0","created":1752844008000,"text":"Pflotran","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlxdyk7s80","created":1753088271766,"text":"一套开源并行代码，用于大规模地下流体流动和反应传输模拟，支持多物理场和多相过程。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqglls0","created":1752844008000,"text":"Mgstat","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlxk56f5c0","created":1753088285227,"text":"一个用干地球物理建模的工具，支持不确定性分析和地质属性的反演","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqg5oo0","created":1752844008000,"text":"geochemFoam","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlyf5rvlk0","created":1753088352744,"text":"基于OpenFOAM的一个地球化学反应输运模拟工具，结合了流体动力学和地球化学反应功能。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqgins0","created":1752844008000,"text":"MOOSE","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlyjnzunk0","created":1753088362552,"text":"多物理场面向对象模拟环境，一个用于模拟多物理场耦合的灵活平台。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqg2rs0","created":1752844008000,"text":"STOMP","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlyqyfmrs0","created":1753088378421,"text":"“地下多相输运”，这是一个用于模拟多相和多组分流体流动及反应性输运的代码，广泛应用于环境工程和资源管理领域。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqgfrc0","created":1752844008000,"text":"SGeMS","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlz2ulz4w0","created":1753088404311,"text":"斯坦福地球统计学建模软件，用于地质属性的建模和模拟。这是一款多物理场仿真软件，","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7ccqgc880","created":1752844008000,"text":"COMSOL","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlz5t6n5k0","created":1753088410755,"text":"为各种物理和化学过程的建模和模拟提供解决方案，包括流体流动、热传递和反应传输，广泛应用于科学研究领域","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbhlws0uhi00","created":1753088224015,"text":"CMG","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhlww0yh1s0","created":1753088232729,"text":"计算机建模组提供先进的软件解决方案用于油藏模拟，支持多相流体流动和复杂的反应传输过程。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7c0eyz8w0","created":1752843981184,"text":"应用领域","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf7c6jrthk0","created":1752843994535,"text":"CO2-水-岩石相互作用","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhm0zn8zaw0","created":1753088554064,"text":"具体分析了CO2的储存量和矿化过程","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbhm1wyuoxc0","created":1753088626600,"text":"四种主要的捕获机制(水动力、溶质性、残留和矿物捕获)及其时空变化。Izgec等人(2008)在较短的模拟周期内分析了影响CO2储存效率的因素，强调了与矿物捕获和吸附相比，流体溶解的重要性。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbhm2938wps0","created":1753088652988,"text":"地层中的总CO2储存量和效率受到各种因素的影响，如CO2分压、温度、岩石孔隙度和盐水盐度","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbhm2i9sjeg0","created":1753088672974,"text":"CO2注入对原生地层岩石的改造可以改变地层的化学成分和孔隙结构","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7c6jrfmo0","created":1752843994535,"text":"CO2泄漏风险评估","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhm34mwdcw0","created":1753088721655,"text":"模拟结果表明，CO2通过裂缝向盖层运移会降低pH值，使盖层中的方解石明显溶解，孔隙度明显增加，孔隙含水量高时方解石会重新形成并重新封闭盖层孔隙。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbhm3ff4eq80","created":1753088745130,"text":"CO2腐蚀井筒并导致泄漏的过程也可以通过RTM进行预测","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7c6jrcwg0","created":1752843994535,"text":"CO2泄漏对环境的潜在影响","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhm3xa1too0","created":1753088784005,"text":"CO2泄漏可能导致浅层含水层污染，重金属污染物释放，甚至对地表人类生存构成威胁","note":"Wang和Jaffe(2004)通过考虑含水层仅由石英、方解石和方铅矿组成，开发了RTM，简化了地球化学系统，以评估CO2泄漏对地下水的负面影响。结果表明，CO2泄漏导致地下水pH值下降，方铅矿大量溶解，水中铅离子浓度升高","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7cuxbqcg0","created":1752844047598,"text":"从孔隙尺度到储层尺度的放大方法","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf7czwd14g0","created":1752844058423,"text":"尺度依赖性","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf7d1j8ydc0","created":1752844061984,"text":"矿物溶解速率","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhmaizvc4g0","created":1753089301464,"text":"野外开采的矿物溶解速率可能比实验室测量值低4-5个数量级","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7d1j8wd40","created":1752844061984,"text":"弥散度","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhmfdu5oyg0","created":1753089682055,"text":"纵向分散性随溶质传输距离增加而增加","note":"从物理本质上讲，弥散度反映了多孔介质对溶质运移的\"分散能力\"。高弥散度意味着溶质在介质中运移时会快速扩散，形成平缓的浓度过渡带；低弥散度则导致溶质保持相对集中的运移前沿\n例如，在地下水污染预测中，较大的αL值会导致污染物羽流在流动方向上更快扩散，形成较长的污染带","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbhmfxwx9hs0","created":1753089725758,"text":"现场尺度(以公里为单位测量)的扩散系数往往超过实验室尺度观测到的扩散系数","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7d1j900w0","created":1752844061984,"text":"水力传导张量","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbhmicgf2eo0","created":1753089914140,"text":"水力导电性(K)随尺度有显著变化","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf7czwcwwg0","created":1752844058423,"text":"放大方法","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf7czwcwwg0","c